"```sql\nSELECT p2.Title, pl.LinkTypeId\nFROM posts p1\nJOIN postLinks pl ON p1.Id = pl.PostId\nJOIN posts p2 ON pl.RelatedPostId = p2.Id\nWHERE p1.Title = 'What are principal component scores?';\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the titles of related posts and their link type IDs for the post titled \"What are principal component scores?\" by joining the `posts` and `postLinks` tables based on the foreign key relationships."